{"tid":845785,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"中國足協成立國足集訓隊　球員需集訓3個半月兼接受軍訓","createTime":"2018-10-03T02:45:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T01:51:48.000Z","uid":3454,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"d33e3ad171b0a65d8c42e5aa2dbb2c31366aff6f","tid":845785,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:45:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181002/s00006/1538490154739\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181002%2Fs00006%2F1538490154739&d=vafsAJtW1FASTd9W%2FbGZwgHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=266f462a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181002%2Fs00006%2F1538490154739&h=4f76c867\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181002/s00006/1538490154739</a><br />\n<br />\n中國足協今晚突然宣布組成一支55人的「國足集訓隊」，入選的球員不但要隨隊集訓3個半月而未能參與所屬球會的賽事，更要接受嚴格軍訓，而消息指這支集訓隊不排除明年參戰中超。<br />\n<br />\n國足今日公布了本月中出戰友賽的23人大軍後，突然宣布另外組成一支「國足集訓隊」，共有55人入選，遍及多支中超及中甲球會，當中包括張修維及廖力生等中國新星。<br />\n<br />\n不過，這支集訓隊的定位耐人尋味，皆因入選球員將由下周一起，連續隨隊集訓長達3個半月，意味將無法再為所屬球會出戰今季餘下賽事，而這55人中有部分球員均為球會主力。此外，集訓隊除了有一般足球員的訓練課程外，更需要接受軍訓，消息指表現較差的球員有可能中途被淘汰。而據指足協更不排除以國足集訓隊的名義，明年參戰中超，甚至出國參加其他國家的賽事。<br />\n<br />\n對此內地網民紛紛表達不滿，有人明言「如果國家隊去踢中超，以後就不看了」，有人直指「完全沒有契約和法制精神」，更有人慨嘆「誰可憐一下中國足球？職業足球不職業，好好的年輕球員不踢聯賽去集中營訓練？有病！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac44597af441825d3a518819cd2f6e097b667e5f","tid":845785,"uid":61660,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:47:18.000Z","msg":"告上FIFA都得啦咁<br />\n不過有冇人夠膽告<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"384df2254a02107d5d2cd2c939ac2a5ed849c441","tid":845785,"uid":126312,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:49:18.000Z","msg":"魔鬼隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19682ff7f0411a6e111e790ce55ffa9fd51afca0","tid":845785,"uid":60281,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:50:26.000Z","msg":"自從打唔贏香港<br />\n中國足球就痴撚左線"},{"pid":"ead48d3d889698ef0db168dd7fed72ad99a39416","tid":845785,"uid":90742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:50:28.000Z","msg":"應該個個都表現差等踢出隊"},{"pid":"c12d34272a869e8d42b8077ee9016f1fe69db3d5","tid":845785,"uid":106929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:58:43.000Z","msg":"軍訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1349d16a593ec5c61523469eea119b8dcd33236b","tid":845785,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T03:03:04.000Z","msg":"大家鬥屎博踢出隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7401d0af9325c8b16bf9ad621a9eb5dfbacd50c","tid":845785,"uid":59966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T03:09:27.000Z","msg":"冇外援邊夠料打中超<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f9170458a109cf9c4d388c0bb042fba88f69a8","tid":845785,"uid":23058,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T03:16:55.000Z","msg":"咁樣訓練work的話 北韓贏左世界杯喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"852565d6b7094ebd9e4791de8b2bbe3e8f3e3888","tid":845785,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3f9170458a109cf9c4d388c0bb042fba88f69a8","tid":845785,"uid":23058,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T03:16:55.000Z","msg":"咁樣訓練work的話 北韓贏左世界杯喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj